These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-6-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, fonseca
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, scientific
House: cottage, tower
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, coach
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: poppy, tulip
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, nectarine
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, orange
1. the person watching scientific movies is not the tower house##6
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the doctor is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
5. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
6. the cottage house is the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |
| Beverage      | fonseca   | prince |
| Hobby         | scientific | time-travel       |
| Music-Genre   | cottage | tower       |
| Nationality   | doctor | coach     |
| Pet           | poppy    | tulip         |
| Sport         | pineapple | nectarine        |
| Transport     | ivory | orange         |

